{"tid":1278422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"屌你老母過咗一日就捉鬼 你地對唔對得住琴晚班義士？","createTime":"2019-07-02T12:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T16:59:20.000Z","uid":112282,"like":618,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"0cd89f0f50fc572f5dbcf0769033da51ed971830","tid":1278422,"uid":112282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:32:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1278298/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1278298/</a><br />\n條片明顯剪過 屈前線義士推走白頭忠係鬼<br />\n之後班狗用滅火筒想整熄煙霧餅 又話佢地扔催淚彈<br />\n大佬啊 你推post比正皮之前 禁入去用下你個腦<br />\n睇清楚先好唔好啊<br />\n你地咁樣對唔對住前線班人啊 又話齊上齊落<br />\n過左唔夠24個鐘係到推埋啲無腦捉鬼facebook片<br />\nfactcheck唔記得哂啦？"},{"pid":"83aaa69271d8c4f461bc354c5081747129391087","tid":1278422,"uid":112282,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:39:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_fNYPZze5bY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_fNYPZze5bY&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPqzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=1b4370ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_fNYPZze5bY</a>"},{"pid":"f90fc99320698a7ca684de45a603dad397b65a61","tid":1278422,"uid":112282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:39:29.000Z","msg":"幫我推呢個post上去<br />\n唔該咁多位"},{"pid":"706816a6bd727683d712cd0cbcf4c5cf259df8c0","tid":1278422,"uid":112282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:41:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d08d34863c48bade1cdb7dc1832716f066b6b511","tid":1278422,"uid":180124,"like":108,"dislike":0,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:41:09.000Z","msg":"話推白頭佬係鬼既人就係仆街"},{"pid":"357d8ae3b38649b9f8f359eacbfe57caeed90834","tid":1278422,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"67e6e46988a8107a607cca88c1d78a8720e3ce07","tid":1278422,"uid":267093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T12:41:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e43ba5a4022e3590c0ed70b6